        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "Temporal scope adds a time dimension to facts in Knowledge Bases ( KBs ) . <S>",
            "relation": "CONTRAST"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "These time scopes specify the time periods ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "when a given fact was valid in real life . <S>",
            "relation": "CONDITION"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "Without temporal scope , ",
            "relation": "CONDITION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "many facts are under-specified , ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "reducing the usefulness of the data for upper level applications such as Question Answering . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "Existing methods for temporal scope inference and extraction still suffer from low accuracy . <S>",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "In this paper , we present a new method ",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "that leverages temporal profiles augmented with context\u2014 Contextual Temporal Profiles ( CTPs ) of entities . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "Through change patterns in an entity's CTP , ",
            "relation": "MANNER-MEANS"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "we model the entity's state change ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "brought about by real world events ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 12,
            "text": "that happen to the entity ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "( e.g , hired , fired , divorced , etc. ) . <S>",
            "relation": "EXEMPLIFICATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "This leads to a new formulation of the temporal scoping problem as a state change detection problem . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "Our experiments show ",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "that this formulation of the problem , and the resulting solution are highly effective ",
            "relation": "EVALUATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "for inferring temporal scope of facts . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        }
    ]
}